21 July 2010President Jacob Zuma will on Thursday, 22 July brief members of the media on the outcomes of the Cabinet Lekgotla which took place from Tuesday, 20 July 2010 at the Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria.Members of the media are invited as follows:-Date: Thursday, 22 July 2010 Time: 08h30 for 09h00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaThere will be a video link to Imbizo Media Centre in Parliament, Cape Town.Please RSVP to:Pheliswa Sebati Cell: 082 413 4609orTuso Zibula Cell: 072 127 1565 before 08h00 on Thursday, 22 July 2010.For media enquiries contact:Bongiwe Gambu Cell: 082 714 9463Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)